skipRecord

public boolean skipRecord(org.gbif.datatester.GenericRecord genericRecord)

Indicates if a GenericRecord should be skipped for some reason. This method is implemented according to the RecordFilter interface from the DataTester framework and is not supposed to be called from any other context except the GenericRecordSet implementation being used.

Specified by:
